outline.text: Armed Forces Canada, Europe, Africa, Middle East

bestPractices.practice: This field is required for posters, presentation/webcasts and proceedings articles.
First select a country. Then, state/province information for that country will appear.

For some countries, there is no ability to select state/province information. Since OpenSky has incomplete state/province information, you may put the state/province information in the Notes to OpenSky field. New terms will be added once verified.

practice.link1: event name, start date, end date, city, state

bestPractices.practice: If providing event or publisher information for other resource types, be sure to complete all event fields: event name, start date, end date, city, state and country.
Washington DC, United States: Enter District of Columbia as the state.
